  "number": "1.8.3",
  "title": "Temperature Conversions",
  "body": " Temperature Conversions  These formulas allow you to convert temperatures between different scales. :       Celsius to Fahrenheit   ° F = 9\/5 ( ° C) + 32     Kelvin to Fahrenheit   ° F = 9\/5 (K - 273) + 32     Fahrenheit to Celsius   ° C = 5\/9 (° F - 32)     Celsius to Kelvin   K = ° C + 273     Kelvin to Celsius   ° C = K - 273     Fahrenheit to Kelvin   K = 5\/9 (° F - 32) + 273     "
